data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Virginia Beach! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2 1/2-bathroom residence is a true gem, boasting a prime location near Landstown Commons Shopping Center and the vibrant local farmer's market. Step into modern living with fully paid off solar panels, ensuring your summer electric bills stay low. Revel in the luxury of new stainless steel appliances (2020) and a large kitchen featuring a brand-new butcher-block countertop on the island (2024). The primary bedroom welcomes you with fresh carpeting (2021), while the primary bath boasts a chic new shower tile (2021) for added elegance. Experience outdoor bliss on the new deck (2021), great for entertaining and enjoying the Virginia Beach sunshine. The house is not just beautiful but also practical, with a new roof (2022), updated vinyl wrapping, and gutters (2023), ensuring low-maintenance living for years to come. Don't miss the chance to make this meticulously updated home yours!
